<span id="Description"></span>
==Описание==

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
Defines an internally generated body heat given in W/kg.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
{{VersionPlus|1.0}}: Can also define the heat source in W.
</div>

